  "body": "This fixes another small regression introduced in 0.62.0. For the full list of changes in 0.62, see [here](https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/releases/tag/v0.62.0).\r\n\r\n<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at v0.62.2 -->\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n### Fixes 🔧\r\n* Fix the waiting status display for synchronous operations by @stefanhaller in https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/pull/5659\r\n\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/jesseduffield/lazygit/compare/v0.62.1...v0.62.2\r\n\r\n",
